      <title>亚马逊反托拉斯案转向关键问题：谁是竞争对手？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/amazon-antitrust-case-turns-to-key-issue-who-are-its-rivals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名机构律师告诉法官，联邦贸易委员会仍在确定谁认为是Amazon.com Inc.的竞争对手，其2023年具有里程碑意义的反托拉斯诉讼指责这家电子商务巨头垄断在线市场服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/amazon-antitrust-case-turns-to-key-issue-who-are-its-rivals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 23:45:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Google可以根据反托拉斯计划保留人为AI投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/google-can-keep-anthropic-ai-investment-under-antitrust-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc.的Google可以保留其在人工智能初创公司（如Anthropic）等人工智能初创公司的现有投资，但要求在周五在该机构Landmark Antrarp Antroust案中提交的修订后的司法部提案，在对任何AI公司进行投资之前，都需要通知反托拉斯的执行者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/google-can-keep-anthropic-ai-investment-under-antitrust-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 23:38:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
